ee it all go down, but they were only gyuides and had not the ability to see it happen. Only the GM can. *sigh*<br>
Oh well, be careful, they are coming out of the woodworks. Later, thanks again.<br>
<br>
LopDrop <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fayrnn>Fayrnn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>When in doubt and Hell <br>overruns your ranks,<br>
