<br>
If you express interest in the sword, they say they will sell it for 200k, or trade it for a Truthbringer stone.  They hope you will then go buy the stone from their other bazaar mule at 75k.  If you do, they vanish with the sword and your 75k.<br>
<br>
I believe I remember reading about this scam on the soapbox here. <p>Hunter Gyre Redbranch<br>

